    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Current Fuel Prices — US Map\"\nsubtitle: \"PADD-region retail gasoline, most recent weekly snapshot\"\n---\n\n\n\n::: {.callout-note appearance=\"simple\"}\nRetail regular gasoline by **PADD region** (Petroleum Administration for\nDefense District). Each state is shaded by its PADD's weekly price.\nSource: EIA weekly retail-price survey. Cadence: weekly.\n:::\n\n## Current PADD retail gasoline {#map}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"plotly html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-93f0a03b18f52ddc19fc\" style=\"width:100%;height:325px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-93f0a03b18f52ddc19fc\">{\"x\":{\"visdat\":{\"6ad33e476a8b\":[\"function () \",\"plotlyVisDat\"]},\"cur_data\":\"6ad33e476a8b\",\"attrs\":{\"6ad33e476a8b\":{\"locationmode\":\"USA-states\",\"locations\":{},\"z\":{},\"text\":{},\"hoverinfo\":\"text\",\"colorscale\":[[\"0\",\"#2f9e44\"],[\"0.5\",\"#fcbf49\"],[\"1\",\"#bc4749\"]],\"colorbar\":{\"title\":\"$/gal\",\"tickformat\":\".2f\"},\"alpha_stroke\":1,\"sizes\":[10,100],\"spans\":[1,20],\"type\":\"choropleth\"}},\"layout\":{\"margin\":{\"b\":40,\"l\":60,\"t\":25,\"r\":10},\"title\":{\"text\":\"Retail regular gasoline by PADD region — April 2026\",\"x\":0.5,\"xanchor\":\"center\"},\"geo\":{\"scope\":\"usa\",\"projection\":{\"type\":\"albers usa\"},\"showlakes\":true,\"lakecolor\":\"#ffffff\"},\"scene\":{\"zaxis\":{\"title\":\"price\"}},\"hovermode\":\"closest\",\"showlegend\":false,\"legend\":{\"yanchor\":\"top\",\"y\":0.5}},\"source\":\"A\",\"config\":{\"modeBarButtonsToAdd\":[\"hoverclosest\",\"hovercompare\"],\"showSendToCloud\":false,\"displayModeBar\":false},\"data\":[{\"colorbar\":{\"title\":\"$/gal\",\"ticklen\":2,\"tickformat\":\".2f\",\"len\":0.5,\"lenmode\":\"fraction\",\"y\":1,\"yanchor\":\"top\"},\"colorscale\":[[\"0\",\"#2f9e44\"],[\"0.5\",\"#fcbf49\"],[\"1\",\"#bc4749\"]],\"showscale\":true,\"locationmode\":\"USA-states\",\"locations\":[\"AK\",\"AZ\",\"CA\",\"HI\",\"NV\",\"OR\",\"WA\"],\"z\":[5.3769999999999998,5.3769999999999998,5.3769999999999998,5.3769999999999998,5.3769999999999998,5.3769999999999998,5.3769999999999998],\"text\":[\"<b>AK<\\/b><br>PADD 5<br>Price: $5.377/gal\",\"<b>AZ<\\/b><br>PADD 5<br>Price: $5.377/gal\",\"<b>CA<\\/b><br>PADD 5<br>Price: $5.377/gal\",\"<b>HI<\\/b><br>PADD 5<br>Price: $5.377/gal\",\"<b>NV<\\/b><br>PADD 5<br>Price: $5.377/gal\",\"<b>OR<\\/b><br>PADD 5<br>Price: $5.377/gal\",\"<b>WA<\\/b><br>PADD 5<br>Price: $5.377/gal\"],\"hoverinfo\":[\"text\",\"text\",\"text\",\"text\",\"text\",\"text\",\"text\"],\"type\":\"choropleth\",\"marker\":{\"line\":{\"color\":\"rgba(31,119,180,1)\"}},\"frame\":null}],\"highlight\":{\"on\":\"plotly_click\",\"persistent\":false,\"dynamic\":false,\"selectize\":false,\"opacityDim\":0.20000000000000001,\"selected\":{\"opacity\":1},\"debounce\":0},\"shinyEvents\":[\"plotly_hover\",\"plotly_click\",\"plotly_selected\",\"plotly_relayout\",\"plotly_brushed\",\"plotly_brushing\",\"plotly_clickannotation\",\"plotly_doubleclick\",\"plotly_deselect\",\"plotly_afterplot\",\"plotly_sunburstclick\"],\"base_url\":\"https://plot.ly\"},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## By PADD region {#table}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"reactable html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-9d411f0009283b0bf049\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-9d411f0009283b0bf049\">{\"x\":{\"tag\":{\"name\":\"Reactable\",\"attribs\":{\"data\":{\"padd\":[\"PADD 5\"],\"current\":[5.377],\"prior_week\":[5.396],\"wow_change\":[-0.019]},\"columns\":[{\"id\":\"padd\",\"name\":\"Region\",\"type\":\"character\",\"minWidth\":180},{\"id\":\"current\",\"name\":\"Current ($/gal)\",\"type\":\"numeric\",\"format\":{\"cell\":{\"digits\":3},\"aggregated\":{\"digits\":3}},\"style\":{\"fontWeight\":600}},{\"id\":\"prior_week\",\"name\":\"Prior week ($/gal)\",\"type\":\"numeric\",\"format\":{\"cell\":{\"digits\":3},\"aggregated\":{\"digits\":3}}},{\"id\":\"wow_change\",\"name\":\"Δ WoW\",\"type\":\"numeric\",\"format\":{\"cell\":{\"digits\":3},\"aggregated\":{\"digits\":3}},\"style\":[{\"color\":\"#2f9e44\",\"fontWeight\":600}]}],\"defaultSorted\":[{\"id\":\"current\",\"desc\":true}],\"highlight\":true,\"striped\":true,\"compact\":true,\"theme\":{\"borderColor\":\"#dee2e6\"},\"dataKey\":\"0c839c1bf55829f5f8da2f302b455165\"},\"children\":[]},\"class\":\"reactR_markup\"},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n## Why PADD and not state?\n\nEIA publishes weekly retail gasoline at the **5 PADD regions**\ncomprehensively. State-level weekly coverage exists for only ~10 states.\nFor a complete national picture without geographic holes, PADD aggregation\nis the honest choice. Every state in a PADD shares the same color because\nthey share the same weekly aggregate.\n",
